## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="9b833-102">加入時`WebReference`物件中的 Web 服務[!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)]，建立檔案的 Web 服務探索處理序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b833-102">When adding a `WebReference` object to a Web service in the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)], files are created by the Web service discovery process.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9b833-103">Web 服務用戶端了解如何尋找 Web 服務描述 (WSDL) 文件，藉由新增`WebReference`物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b833-103">Web service clients learn where to find the Web service description (WSDL) document by adding a `WebReference` object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9b833-104">Web 服務用戶端然後儲存探索文件至磁碟使用`WriteAll`方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b833-104">The Web service clients then save the discovered documents to the disk by using the `WriteAll` method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9b833-105">例如，探索到的文件可能.xsd 結構描述檔案或服務描述。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b833-105">For example, the discovered documents may be .xsd schema files or service descriptions.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9b833-106">在此程序結束時，用戶端刪除的檔案。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b833-106">At the end of the process, the client deletes the files.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9b833-107">您可以變更預設位置的暫存資料夾中的檔案使用`tempFilesLocation`切換移入`<xmlSerializer>`Machine.config 組態檔，如下列範例中所指定的元素。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b833-107">You can change the default location of the files in the temporary folder by using the `tempFilesLocation` switch in the `<xmlSerializer>` element, specified in the Machine.config configuration file, as in the following example.</span></span>  
  
```  
<configuration>  
  <system.web>  
  <system.xml.serialization>  
    <xmlSerializer tempFilesLocation=".."/>  
  </system.xml.serialization>  
</configuration>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9b833-108">值`tempFilesLocation`必須是絕對路徑。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b833-108">The value of `tempFilesLocation` must be an absolute path.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9b833-109">如果指定的路徑不是絕對的[!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)]產生<xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationErrorsException>時參考的組態區段的例外狀況。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b833-109">If the path specified is not absolute, the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] generates a <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationErrorsException> exception when the configuration section is referenced.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9b833-110">屬性的值會截斷為移除開頭和尾端空白字元。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b833-110">The value of the property is truncated to remove leading and trailing white spaces.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9b833-111">如果值`tempFilesLocation`屬性由空白字元組成，預設的 %TMP%位置在進行編譯。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b833-111">If value of the `tempFilesLocation` property is composed of white space, the default %TMP% location is used for the compilation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9b833-112">若未，就會發生相同的預設行為`tempFilesLocation`指定參數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b833-112">The same default behavior occurs when no `tempFilesLocation` switch is specified.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9b833-113"><xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer>不會檢查以查看該路徑是否存在。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b833-113">The <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> does not check to see whether the path exists.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9b833-114">如果沒有，<xref:System.IO.DirectoryNotFoundException>產生。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b833-114">If it does not, a <xref:System.IO.DirectoryNotFoundException> is generated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9b833-115">這是相同的預設行為`XmlSerializer`如果 %TMP%路徑不存在。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b833-115">This is identical to the default behavior of the `XmlSerializer` if the %TMP% path does not exist.</span></span>  
  
